node.text:
We’re super excited to be Introducing our new I Sculpt I Shade Brow Collection. 
Achieve a defined brow with our quick and easy transformative brow products which comes in Brow Pencils , Brow Pens, Brow Gels and our multi- Functional Palette . 

I Sculpt I Shade Brow Pencil is an Ultra Thin pencil with built in brush that provides an easy glide on application with every stroke. Super Long Lasting and Smudge Proof. 

**I Sculpt I Shade Brow Pen is a transformative micro sculpting and shading pen that provides thin hairlike controlled strokes to the brows. Results are outstanding. Formula is Vegan, Fragrance Free, Paraben Free and Cruelty Free

**I sculpt I Shade Brow Gel is a lightweight highly pigmented gel formula that defines and adds dimension to the brows . 

**I Sculpt I Shade Palette is a 4 pan universal and multifunctional powder palette. This finely milled matte shades help create fuller brows. Can also be used to create soft chocolate Smokey eye looks. 

I Sculpt I Shade Brow Pencil-$10 
I Sculpt I Shade Brow Pen -$14
I Sculpt I Shade Brow Gel -$12
I Sculpt I Shade Palette - $10

I Sculpt I Shade Brow Products are - 
* Super Long wearing
* Smudge Proof and Water Proof
* Glides on Easily 
* Very thin Tips to aid controlled application and mimic hair like strokes. 
* Brow Gel visibly thickens the brow while aiding definition

Just Launched on our website-www.Juviasplace.com

Launches on Ulta Beauty website August 15th
